<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7476> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7476" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cos. suff. 33. Monetalis. In MRR 2.455, and Index, 635, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.457, no. 436, 52 B.C. He was proconsul of Asia, perhaps in 28-27 (Syme, Historia 11, 1962, 147148-RP 2.532). See Wiseman, NM 274, no. 494. He was tribune of the plebs in 51 (MRR 2.241). (TJC)\n" ;
	dprr:hasID 7476 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6458> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6458" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Entered office on September 1 (Fast. Ven., Degrassi 251, 254f.; Fad. Mag. Vic., ibid., 283, 288, cf. ibid. 136, 508f.; CIL 9.1554-1.740; cf. RE 17.2.1429, no. 74). See PIR 3.435, no. 443; Von Premerstemi, JOEAI 28 (1933) 147, note 15." ;
	dprr:hasID 6458 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5383> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5383" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Vetoed an anti-Caesarian resolution of the Senate (Cael. in Cic. Fam. 8.8.6). See Lübker no. 1; PIR 3.435." ;
	dprr:hasID 5383 .
